{
  "stem": "893.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was on my-- I was-- I was using my youngest brother's papers, so actually, my papers said that I was 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- no, with my brother's--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--name.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even though I looked too old to be 14 or 15.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you know, Slovakians, they were very simple people, and they were not as sophisticated as-- as Americans or-- or Germans were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in-- in the city of [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Debrecen ?] when the war was over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the meantime, my cousin, who lived in Brooklyn, who was a first cousin, who was born in the same city, found our names at the-- on the survivor's list.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- she could write letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She sent us currency, $10 bills, in the letter and also packages, whatever came through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was-- she wanted us-- she said, if no one else survived, she wants us to come to the States.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no consular representation in the war zone in Slovakia, especially in-- in areas that were occupied by Russians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we would-- in order to get to the United States, we would have had to go to a-- a country that had a continuous United States representation.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Switzerland was out of the question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wouldn't give us a visa unless they were sure that we could-- we could get out of-- and even Paris didn't have consular representation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had delegation, and they had headquarters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we had to go either to Spain or to a-- a country that had-- my cousins were very friendly with the Reichmanns of Toronto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You've heard of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time, they lived in Tangier, Morocco.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were bankers there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they asked them to arrange a visa to Tangier, Morocco.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, it was an international zone.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
